      </hazardstatement>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Please Note</title>
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Electrical equipment
should only be installed, operated, serviced, and maintained by qualified
personnel. No responsibility is assumed by Schneider Electric for
any consequences arising out of the use of this material.</p>
            <p class="- topic/p ">A
qualified person is one who has skills and knowledge related to the
construction, installation, and operation of electrical equipment
and has received safety training to recognize and avoid the hazards
involved.</p>
         </sectiondiv>
